&lt;div id="ebnIxs"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="productcard:12345336"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="QQSR7P"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="productcard:12113209"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="Fnwh64"&gt;The consoles still aren’t cheap, per se, but they’re as cheap as you’ll find for machines that can play the latest titles with up to 4K resolution and 120 frames per second. &lt;/p&gt;
