      &lt;img alt="Illustration of the Threads app logo" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JC8jZ7Ms9Phwn-RqVWlTa2QvKyg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73641593/STK156_Instagram_threads_2.0.jpg" /&gt;
